{"id":19,"date":"2025-12-12T19:00:11","date_gmt":"2025-12-12T19:00:11","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.formajewelry.com\/?page_id=19"},"modified":"2026-05-22T18:31:21","modified_gmt":"2026-05-22T18:31:21","slug":"home","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/www.formajewelry.com\/","title":{"rendered":"Home"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<div class=\"wp-block-uagb-container uagb-block-7d5145f7 alignfull uagb-is-root-container\"><div class=\"uagb-container-inner-blocks-wrap\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"588\" src=\"https:\/\/www.formajewelry.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/ghjhgjh-1024x588.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-130\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.formajewelry.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/ghjhgjh-1024x588.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/www.formajewelry.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/ghjhgjh-300x172.jpg 300w, https:\/\/www.formajewelry.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/ghjhgjh-768x441.jpg 768w, https:\/\/www.formajewelry.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/ghjhgjh-1536x882.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/www.formajewelry.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/ghjhgjh.jpg 1913w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-uagb-container uagb-block-8d6b040b alignfull uagb-is-root-container\"><div class=\"uagb-container-inner-blocks-wrap\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-uagb-advanced-heading uagb-block-d11973ff\"><h3 class=\"uagb-heading-text\">In this hands-on wax carving workshop, you\u2019ll explore tools and techniques to create a one-of-a-kind jewelry piece. Beginners are welcome, no prior experience is necessary.<br>Couples ring experiences, private one-on-one sessions, group gatherings, and corporate workshops are available &#8211; click to explore all workshop experiences<\/h3><\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-uagb-container uagb-block-286a75a0 alignfull uagb-is-root-container\"><div class=\"uagb-container-inner-blocks-wrap\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-uagb-container uagb-block-a2fb2b83\">\t\t\t\t\t<div\n\t\t\t\t\t\tclass=\"wp-block-uagb-image-gallery uagb-block-d4a4b774     \"\n\t\t\t\t\t\tstyle=\"\"\n\t\t\t\t\t>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"spectra-image-gallery spectra-image-gallery__layout--grid spectra-image-gallery__layout--grid-col-3 spectra-image-gallery__layout--grid-col-tab-3 spectra-image-gallery__layout--grid-col-mob-2\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"spectra-image-gallery__media-wrapper\" data-spectra-gallery-image-id=\"175\" tabindex=\"0\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"spectra-image-gallery__media spectra-image-gallery__media--grid\">\n\t\t\t\t<picture>\n\t\t\t\t\t<source media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.formajewelry.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/L1025590-1024x1024.jpg\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<source media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.formajewelry.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/L1025590-1024x1024.jpg\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" class=\"spectra-image-gallery__media-thumbnail spectra-image-gallery__media-thumbnail--grid\" src=\"https:\/\/www.formajewelry.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/L1025590-300x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" \/>\n\t\t\t\t<\/picture>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"spectra-image-gallery__media-thumbnail-blurrer\"><\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"spectra-image-gallery__media-thumbnail-caption-wrapper spectra-image-gallery__media-thumbnail-caption-wrapper--overlay\"><\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"spectra-image-gallery__media-wrapper\" data-spectra-gallery-image-id=\"171\" tabindex=\"0\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"spectra-image-gallery__media spectra-image-gallery__media--grid\">\n\t\t\t\t<picture>\n\t\t\t\t\t<source media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.formajewelry.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/L1025579-1024x1024.jpg\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<source media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.formajewelry.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/L1025579-1024x1024.jpg\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" class=\"spectra-image-gallery__media-thumbnail spectra-image-gallery__media-thumbnail--grid\" src=\"https:\/\/www.formajewelry.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/L1025579-300x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" \/>\n\t\t\t\t<\/picture>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"spectra-image-gallery__media-thumbnail-blurrer\"><\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"spectra-image-gallery__media-thumbnail-caption-wrapper spectra-image-gallery__media-thumbnail-caption-wrapper--overlay\"><\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"spectra-image-gallery__media-wrapper\" data-spectra-gallery-image-id=\"174\" tabindex=\"0\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"spectra-image-gallery__media spectra-image-gallery__media--grid\">\n\t\t\t\t<picture>\n\t\t\t\t\t<source media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.formajewelry.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/L1025600-1024x1024.jpg\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<source media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.formajewelry.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/L1025600-1024x1024.jpg\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" class=\"spectra-image-gallery__media-thumbnail spectra-image-gallery__media-thumbnail--grid\" src=\"https:\/\/www.formajewelry.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/L1025600-300x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" \/>\n\t\t\t\t<\/picture>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"spectra-image-gallery__media-thumbnail-blurrer\"><\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"spectra-image-gallery__media-thumbnail-caption-wrapper spectra-image-gallery__media-thumbnail-caption-wrapper--overlay\"><\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"><\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-uagb-container uagb-block-03351ca9 alignfull uagb-is-root-container\"><div class=\"uagb-container-inner-blocks-wrap\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"466\" src=\"https:\/\/www.formajewelry.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/New-Project-55555-1024x466.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-276\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.formajewelry.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/New-Project-55555-1024x466.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/www.formajewelry.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/New-Project-55555-300x136.jpg 300w, https:\/\/www.formajewelry.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/New-Project-55555-768x349.jpg 768w, https:\/\/www.formajewelry.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/New-Project-55555.jpg 1433w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-uagb-container uagb-block-8isoi5tt alignfull uagb-is-root-container\"><div class=\"uagb-container-inner-blocks-wrap\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-uagb-container uagb-block-avkgdtwm\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-uagb-container uagb-block-lzsgq17u\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-uagb-image alignleft uagb-block-dxbunsqp wp-block-uagb-image--layout-default wp-block-uagb-image--effect-static wp-block-uagb-image--align-left\"><figure class=\"wp-block-uagb-image__figure\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.formajewelry.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/unnamed-29.jpg ,https:\/\/www.formajewelry.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/unnamed-29.jpg 780w, https:\/\/www.formajewelry.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/unnamed-29.jpg 360w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 480px) 150px\" src=\"https:\/\/www.formajewelry.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/unnamed-29.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"uag-image-123\" width=\"368\" height=\"450\" title=\"unnamed-29\" loading=\"lazy\" role=\"img\"\/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-uagb-info-box uagb-block-bqwthfbc uagb-infobox__content-wrap  uagb-infobox-icon-above-title uagb-infobox-image-valign-top\"><div class=\"uagb-ifb-content\"><div class=\"uagb-ifb-title-wrap\"><h3 class=\"uagb-ifb-title\"><strong>1.<\/strong> <strong>Concept &amp; Form<\/strong><\/h3><\/div><p class=\"uagb-ifb-desc\">Translate your ideas from paper to wax. In this 2\u20133 hour session, you will carve a custom jewelry piece, focusing on the organic textures and shapes that surface during the creative process. While based in Lisbon, this workshop is fully portable and can be hosted at a location of your choosing (travel fees applicable).<\/p><\/div><\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-uagb-container uagb-block-v5zhziza\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-uagb-image alignleft uagb-block-pouo8b8t wp-block-uagb-image--layout-default wp-block-uagb-image--effect-static wp-block-uagb-image--align-left\"><figure class=\"wp-block-uagb-image__figure\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.formajewelry.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/unnamed-31.jpg ,https:\/\/www.formajewelry.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/unnamed-31.jpg 780w, https:\/\/www.formajewelry.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/unnamed-31.jpg 360w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 480px) 150px\" src=\"https:\/\/www.formajewelry.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/unnamed-31.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"uag-image-132\" width=\"368\" height=\"450\" title=\"unnamed-31\" loading=\"lazy\" role=\"img\"\/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-uagb-info-box uagb-block-j1a7bn4t uagb-infobox__content-wrap  uagb-infobox-icon-above-title uagb-infobox-image-valign-top\"><div class=\"uagb-ifb-content\"><div class=\"uagb-ifb-title-wrap\"><h3 class=\"uagb-ifb-title\"><strong>2. <strong>Transformation into Metal<\/strong><\/strong><\/h3><\/div><p class=\"uagb-ifb-desc\">Following our session, your wax sculpture is sent to be professionally transitioned into the metal of your choice, immortalizing every hand-carved detail and texture. As each piece is unique, casting fees are independent of the workshop and vary based on the final weight and material; an estimate will be provided during your session to guide your selection.<\/p><\/div><\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-uagb-container uagb-block-thnikdwn\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-uagb-image alignleft uagb-block-tozkrpvw wp-block-uagb-image--layout-default wp-block-uagb-image--effect-static wp-block-uagb-image--align-left\"><figure class=\"wp-block-uagb-image__figure\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.formajewelry.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/unnamed-28.jpg ,https:\/\/www.formajewelry.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/unnamed-28.jpg 780w, https:\/\/www.formajewelry.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/unnamed-28.jpg 360w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 480px) 150px\" src=\"https:\/\/www.formajewelry.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/unnamed-28.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"uag-image-118\" width=\"368\" height=\"450\" title=\"unnamed-28\" loading=\"lazy\" role=\"img\"\/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-uagb-info-box uagb-block-pmb1tc4t uagb-infobox__content-wrap  uagb-infobox-icon-above-title uagb-infobox-image-valign-top\"><div class=\"uagb-ifb-content\"><div class=\"uagb-ifb-title-wrap\"><h3 class=\"uagb-ifb-title\"><strong>3. Back in Your Hands<\/strong><\/h3><\/div><p class=\"uagb-ifb-desc\">Within two weeks, your design returns to you in its final form\u2014carefully refined, polished, and ready to wear. This marks the end of the creative process, leaving you with a lasting, wearable piece of your own artistry.<\/p><\/div><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-uagb-container uagb-block-229b4dd0 alignfull uagb-is-root-container\"><div class=\"uagb-container-inner-blocks-wrap\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-uagb-advanced-heading uagb-block-00f12658\"><h2 class=\"uagb-heading-text\"><strong>Studio Offerings<\/strong>: <em>A collection of workshops designed to bring your ideas to life.<\/em><\/h2><\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-uagb-container uagb-block-4bb677ri alignfull uagb-is-root-container\"><div class=\"uagb-container-inner-blocks-wrap\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-uagb-container uagb-layout-grid uagb-block-qg31irta\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-uagb-container uagb-block-c2xqdmx5\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-uagb-info-box uagb-block-nukjyyh0 uagb-infobox__content-wrap  uagb-infobox-icon-above-title uagb-infobox-image-valign-top\"><div class=\"uagb-ifb-content\"><div class=\"uagb-ifb-title-wrap\"><h3 class=\"uagb-ifb-title\">The Duo Session: <em>A ring making experience for couples. <\/em><br><br><\/h3><\/div><p class=\"uagb-ifb-desc\">An intimate space for two to translate their connection into a pair of handcrafted rings. Each participant carves a wax piece, producing distinct forms that emerge from a shared process.<\/p><\/div><\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-uagb-container uagb-block-ar3dbf0i\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-uagb-info-box uagb-block-3crxawwl uagb-infobox__content-wrap  uagb-infobox-icon-above-title uagb-infobox-image-valign-top\"><div class=\"uagb-ifb-content\"><div class=\"uagb-ifb-title-wrap\"><h3 class=\"uagb-ifb-title\">The Private Dialogue: <em>A dedicated one-on-one mentorship.<\/em><br><\/h3><\/div><p class=\"uagb-ifb-desc\"><br>Explore the art of ring-making with focused, individual attention. This private session is tailored to your pace as you carve a custom ring\u2014perfectly suited for your own hand or as a thoughtful gift for someone else.<\/p><\/div><\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-uagb-container uagb-block-bx2etb6e\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-uagb-info-box uagb-block-0raqxrcm uagb-infobox__content-wrap  uagb-infobox-icon-above-title uagb-infobox-image-valign-top\"><div class=\"uagb-ifb-content\"><div class=\"uagb-ifb-title-wrap\"><h3 class=\"uagb-ifb-title\">The Collective Table: <em>A shared ring-making experience. <\/em><br><br><\/h3><\/div><p class=\"uagb-ifb-desc\">A creative space for groups to gather and celebrate together. Ideal for birthdays, bridal showers, or private milestones, guests carve their own custom rings to mark the occasion.<\/p><\/div><\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-uagb-container uagb-block-jd9kc25i\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-uagb-info-box uagb-block-trbdpwon uagb-infobox__content-wrap  uagb-infobox-icon-above-title uagb-infobox-image-valign-top\"><div class=\"uagb-ifb-content\"><div class=\"uagb-ifb-title-wrap\"><h3 class=\"uagb-ifb-title\">The Object Study: <em>An expansion of the craft.  <\/em><br><br><\/h3><\/div><p class=\"uagb-ifb-desc\">A session dedicated to the exploration of different jewelry forms. From pendants to earrings and brooches, this workshop invites you to carve wax into a custom piece\u2014shaping your own ideas into a wearable object.<\/p><\/div><\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-uagb-container uagb-block-e96jehyc\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-uagb-info-box uagb-block-svk8xcmf uagb-infobox__content-wrap  uagb-infobox-icon-above-title uagb-infobox-image-valign-top\"><div class=\"uagb-ifb-content\"><div class=\"uagb-ifb-title-wrap\"><h3 class=\"uagb-ifb-title\">The Executive: <em>A jewelry-making experience for corporate teams. <\/em><br><br><\/h3><\/div><p class=\"uagb-ifb-desc\">An immersive workshop tailored for professional groups seeking a meaningful way to connect. This session invites participants to explore the meditative craft of wax carving. By designing and shaping custom pieces, your team will engage in a creative process that encourages fresh perspectives, problem-solving, and strengthened professional bonds through a focused, tactile experience.<\/p><\/div><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-uagb-container uagb-block-adf13f54 alignfull uagb-is-root-container\"><div class=\"uagb-container-inner-blocks-wrap\"><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-uagb-container uagb-block-533556e3 alignfull uagb-is-root-container\"><div class=\"uagb-container-inner-blocks-wrap\"><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-uagb-container uagb-block-1d93a987 alignfull uagb-is-root-container\"><div class=\"uagb-container-inner-blocks-wrap\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full is-resized is-style-default\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"700\" height=\"405\" src=\"https:\/\/www.formajewelry.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/New-Project-888888.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-303\" style=\"aspect-ratio:16\/9;object-fit:contain;width:600px\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.formajewelry.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/New-Project-888888.jpg 700w, https:\/\/www.formajewelry.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/New-Project-888888-300x174.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" \/><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-uagb-container uagb-block-cef10e6f alignfull uagb-is-root-container\"><div class=\"uagb-container-inner-blocks-wrap\">\n<header class=\"wp-block-uagb-advanced-heading uagb-block-caa39055\"><h2 class=\"uagb-heading-text\"><strong>How to Book a Workshop<\/strong>:<\/h2><\/header>\n\n\n\n<ol class=\"wp-block-list has-medium-font-size\">\n<li class=\"has-medium-font-size\">Contact us via email cuauatelier@gmail.com<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li class=\"has-medium-font-size\">Let us know which workshop you\u2019re interested in and your preferred dates<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li class=\"has-medium-font-size\">We\u2019ll confirm availability and send booking details<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"740\" src=\"https:\/\/www.formajewelry.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/cuauatelier4-1024x740.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-144\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.formajewelry.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/cuauatelier4-1024x740.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/www.formajewelry.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/cuauatelier4-300x217.jpg 300w, https:\/\/www.formajewelry.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/cuauatelier4-768x555.jpg 768w, https:\/\/www.formajewelry.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/cuauatelier4-1536x1109.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/www.formajewelry.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/cuauatelier4.jpg 1609w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"><\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-uagb-container uagb-block-a43617fb alignfull uagb-is-root-container\"><div class=\"uagb-container-inner-blocks-wrap\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-uagb-container uagb-block-6f4960ab\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-style-rounded wp-duotone-grayscale\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"576\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https:\/\/www.formajewelry.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/L1025898-576x1024.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-381\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.formajewelry.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/L1025898-576x1024.jpg 576w, https:\/\/www.formajewelry.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/L1025898-169x300.jpg 169w, https:\/\/www.formajewelry.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/L1025898-768x1364.jpg 768w, https:\/\/www.formajewelry.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/L1025898-865x1536.jpg 865w, https:\/\/www.formajewelry.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/L1025898-1153x2048.jpg 1153w, https:\/\/www.formajewelry.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/L1025898.jpg 1441w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 576px) 100vw, 576px\" \/><\/figure>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-uagb-container uagb-block-0b003bbe\">\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size wp-block-paragraph\">For me, making is about curiosity, not rules. It\u2019s about getting your hands dirty, finding your rhythm, and the joy of the process itself. I\u2019ve spent the last ten years at the bench turning raw materials into wearable art, and I\u2019m here to help you find your flow and create a piece that is entirely yours.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-uagb-container uagb-block-8bc92581\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-style-default\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" src=\"https:\/\/www.formajewelry.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/L1025550-1-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-292\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.formajewelry.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/L1025550-1-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/www.formajewelry.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/L1025550-1-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/www.formajewelry.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/L1025550-1-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/www.formajewelry.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/L1025550-1-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/www.formajewelry.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/L1025550-1-2048x1366.jpg 2048w, https:\/\/www.formajewelry.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/L1025550-1-150x100.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure>\n<\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-uagb-container uagb-block-892e2e40 alignfull uagb-is-root-container\"><div class=\"uagb-container-inner-blocks-wrap\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-uagb-container uagb-block-a4bd2ffb\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-8f761849 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:25%\"><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:50%\">\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-align-center\"> cuauatelier@gmail.com<\/h2>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:25%\"><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>In this hands-on wax carving workshop, you\u2019ll explore tools and techniques to create a one-of-a-kind jewelry piece. Beginners are welcome, no prior experience is necessary.Couples ring experiences, private one-on-one sessions, group gatherings, and corporate workshops are available &#8211; click to explore all workshop experiences Studio Offerings: A collection of workshops desig